Animation (Interface):
    - addShape
    - removeShape
    - addTransformation
    - removeTransformation // do we need this method?
    - getShapeAtTick?? //implemented in later HW

AnimationImpl (subtype):
    Constructor:
        - shapes (ArrayList<Shape>)
        - transformation (ArrayList<Transformation>)

